# Personal data — your real résumé, real ATS tracker, real contacts. Never committed.
# Only private/README.md (the signpost) is tracked; everything else here is yours alone.
/private/*
!/private/README.md
!/private/.gitkeep
# Belt-and-suspenders: keep résumé artifacts out even if dropped outside private/.
# (data/ats/ self-manages via its own .gitignore — don't blanket-ignore it here.)
**/*.resume.pdf
**/resume.pdf
resume.json
search/private-notes.md
search/private-notes.md
